LOCATION:Tarboro Road Community Center\, 121 N Tarboro St\, Raleigh\, NC 27
 610\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Try Bike Polo! + Alley Cat
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
